{
  "stem": "20684.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was fantastic.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was such a fascinating thing, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The thing came up and got bigger and bigger and bigger.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then my father told me that I can look now, slowly, slowly, slowly.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But, of course, I was looking all the time, for 10 minutes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He-- I fooled him all right, didn't I?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So that was a way of expressing oneself.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And suddenly the light came on, and after a little while, the party stopped, because some couple of Ukrainian guards found us in the forest.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We're trying to hide in-- under bushes, and so had no chance.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they started talking, you know, about-- to my parents, you know that we're Jews, Jews.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father is no, no we're not.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We're just-- we're-- we're-- he's try to pretend that he-- we're-- we're-- we're not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so he had no papers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He had beard.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And both my-- my parents were hunchbacked then.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They looked a bit like the monkeys I used to go and see at-- in the zoo, because they hadn't straightened up for 13 months.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Took them for a while.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My mother never recovered.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She's always had the-- had a-- her back was permanently this sort of bent, humped.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And my father, well, didn't live long enough to recover, so.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And as for me, no problem.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I-- I was-- I stood up, just started touching the top-- I grew a couple of inches while I was in the cupboard.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And got much wiser too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were taken into the interrogation and we were forced to-- we were denied the fact that they were Jewish.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I still remember the officer who interrogated us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Ukrainians took us to a village-- Was it--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--and he was in charge.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
